{"tid":1529430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動post】想幫狗鐵洗白？","createTime":"2019-09-01T17:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T09:23:22.000Z","uid":175123,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9675aae1fbdba79ff074c7bc30146d5a735871fe","tid":1529430,"uid":175123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:34:04.000Z","msg":"唔係唔得，但你地真係得返一次機會。<br />\n<br />\n721到831，我唔覺得今次抗爭connect到你地班所謂狗鐵同路人/前線黃絲。份工重要，重唔重要得過香港市民，尤其係前線學生條命？<br />\n<br />\n佢地搵命搏，做埋你地有負擔嘅大人嗰份，你地有冇一次大罷工大集會支持返佢匝？人地醫護界喺醫院罷工集會有晒媒體關注，真係有心嘅乜界乜公司都做到，我唔理你地所謂狗鐵黃絲係前線part time小黃人文職定高層<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">趁92 93大三罷去自己總部搞個集會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咁都做唔到嘅話手足真係徹底割狗鐵蓆，freedom is not free，每個人都要犧牲啲嘢先會抗爭成功，咪撚再咁自私"},{"pid":"524309a349943c9c3637cf479777632b6aedb5e0","tid":1529430,"uid":264455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:35:58.000Z","msg":"人話"},{"pid":"6217ae3bbdc3f395bdf99364eeecef8a455f5971","tid":1529430,"uid":175123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:45:11.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"96434dbaeb8452a42c4a7df395b6fc798d9b9538","tid":1529430,"uid":175123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:50:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fee9992b87ae0c8d90c88b17d49f9be51ef23151","tid":1529430,"uid":127373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:51:59.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"a5190ca2a792e00cad192283b7c9d00d4bc60b4d","tid":1529430,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/01/223606_db1fcc72048388792c25c8bdc081a00b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F01%2F223606_db1fcc72048388792c25c8bdc081a00b.gif&h=16fdca9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\